7080317Ba.event_description:
Canada, NWT, April 10 "Restriction of businesses because they are unable or unlikely to maintain proper social (physical) distancing to keep residents safe. The order essentially breaks businesses into red (absolutely not allowed to remain open);
yellow (if you can maintain good social distance and don’t present a high-risk, you can remain
open); and green (businesses that we believe must stay open to protect public health). "

